                  "<p><span id=\"htZoomImageMsg\"></span></p>",
                  {
                     "text": "### Prerequisites\n\nThe first two chapters of the \"First Steps\" section explain how to perform counting and comparisons. Therefore, we recommend studying these chapters before proceeding with this text.",
